flowchart TD
    %% Inline label syntax
    A1 -- solid label --> B1
    A2 -. dotted label .-> B2
    A3 == thick label ==> B3
    %% Pipe label syntax
    C1 -->|pipe label| D1
    C2 -.->|dotted pipe| D2
    C3 ==>|thick pipe| D3
    %% Labels with special chars
    E1 -->|yes / no| F1
    E2 -->|count: 42| F2
